Package org.turbogwt.core.collections

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JsArray<T>
    A more featured extension of JsArray.
    JsArrayIterator<T>
    Iterator implemented under JsArray.
    JsArrayList<T>
    An implementation of List wrapping a JsArray.
    JsArrays
    Many utility methods for dealing with JsArrays.
    JsArraySet<T>
    An implementation of Set underpinned by an array.
    JsHashSet<T>
    An implementation of Set based on JsHashTable.
    JsHashTable<T>
    A hash table implemented on a javascript object.
    JsMap<T>
    Map of String to Object implemented on a JavaScriptObject.
    JsMapBoolean
    Map of String to native boolean implemented on a JavaScriptObject.
    JsMapInteger
    Map of String to native integer implemented on a JavaScriptObject.
    JsMapNumber
    Map of String to native number implemented on a JavaScriptObject.
    JsMapString
    Map of String to String implemented on a JavaScriptObject.
    LightMap<T>
    A Map from String to Object implementation over a Javascript Object.
